          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1618245246779-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped ginger</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further</p><p>Add the <strong>basmati rice</strong> and <strong>Thai stock</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 15-20 min or until the water is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
